# Asterisk Project Overview

**Asterisk** is a dark-themed Markdown note editor built with Electron + React + TypeScript + CodeMirror 6.

## Architecture

Standard Electron architecture with three contexts:

| Context | Location | Role |
|---|----|---|
| Main | `src/main/` | Node.js process - window, menu, file system |
| Preload | `src/preload/` | Bridge exposing API to renderer |
| Renderer | `src/renderer/src/` | React frontend - UI components |

## Directory Structure

```
src/
├── main/
│   ├── index.ts          # Entry: window creation, lifecycle
│   ├── menu.ts           # Application menu setup
│   └── ipc/
│       ├── handlers.ts   # IPC event registration
│       └── fileSystem.ts # File operation handlers
├── preload/
│   ├── index.ts          # Exposes `window.asterisk` API
│   └── types.ts          # TypeScript interfaces
└── renderer/
    ├── index.html        # HTML entry point
    └── src/
        ├── main.tsx      # React entry point
        ├── App.tsx       # Root component, layout
        ├── types/
        │   └── index.ts  # Shared types
        ├── store/
        │   ├── useWorkspace.ts  # Zustand: files, tabs, folders
        │   └── useSettings.ts   # Zustand: themes, typography
        ├── hooks/
        │   ├── useAutoSave.ts   # Auto-save logic
        │   └── useFileOps.ts    # File operations
        ├── styles/
        │   ├── global.css       # Base styles, CSS vars
        │   └── layout.css       # Layout utilities
        └── components/
            ├── TopBar/          # Title bar, window controls
            ├── Sidebar/         # File tree, filter bar
            ├── Editor/          # CodeMirror editor, tabs
            ├── Preview/         # Markdown preview
            ├── StatusBar/       # Bottom status bar
            ├── Settings/        # Settings modal
            └── NeuralGraph/     # Graph visualization
```

## Key Conventions

- **State**: Use Zustand stores (`useWorkspace`, `useSettings`)
- **IPC**: Main process handlers in `src/main/ipc/`, exposed via `window.asterisk`
- **Styling**: CSS files colocated with components (`Component.tsx` + `Component.css`)
- **Build**: `electron-vite` - see `electron.vite.config.ts`

## Running

```bash
npm run dev      # Development with hot reload
npm run build    # Production build
npm run preview  # Preview production build
```

## Key Dependencies

- `@codemirror/*` - Editor functionality
- `marked` - Markdown rendering
- `zustand` - State management
- `lucide-react` - Icons
- `d3` - Graph visualization
